Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:30.44,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Always　 醒めきってた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:33.61,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}速すぎる  Day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:36.73,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}透明な闇に囲まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:40.22,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も似た網の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:43.43,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Found you  あの日の風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:46.67,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揺れ動いたPassion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.10,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}And all of my past
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:53.09,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全てキミに会うためのProcessだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:56.04,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Slowly open up my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:58.66,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}within the blackness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:02.54,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼方から聞こえる予感に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:06.47,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}鼓動奮わせて居たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:10.32,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's unlimited  It's unlimited
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:13.82,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}If I can believe myself again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:17.16,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光の中  目覚めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:20.88,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じてくれたキミとなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.13,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:23.30,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:26.78,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここで生まれ変わる景色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:30.25,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傷さえいま誇りになる
