Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:08.69,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}去往不斷延展的天邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:12.14,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}透明的翅膀將我引領
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:15.67,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}它在遠方靜待著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.77,0:02:21.06,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛往未曾預見的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:30.44,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理智清醒時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:33.61,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}時常感到日夜流逝過快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:36.73,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}四周被透明的黑暗包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:40.22,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我們都活在寸步難移的網中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:43.43,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}尋覓你  每當風吹過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:46.67,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中激情彷彿隨風躍動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:48.10,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}And all of my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:53.09,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一切皆為與你相會的前奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:56.04,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Slowly open up my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:58.66,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}within the blackness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:02.54,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遠方傳來的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:06.47,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}讓我不禁加快心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.32,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's unlimited  It's unlimited
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:13.82,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}If I can believe myself again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:17.16,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光輝灑下  我逐漸甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:20.88,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要你我互信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.13,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:23.30,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:26.78,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眼前景色將煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:30.25,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}昔日傷痕亦成今日榮耀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:34.90,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因此與你一起超越重力的束縛
